OL,7,FA man has been found guilty of raping
OL,8,Fhis ex-girlfriend in an attack in
OL,9,Fwhich he murdered her and her sister
OL,10,Fwith a crossbow and their mother with
OL,11,Fa knife, ITV News Correspondent John
OL,12,FRay brings the latest.
OL,14,FWarning: This report contains details
OL,15,Fsome people may find distressing.
OL,17,FTriple killer Kyle Clifford has been
OL,18,Fconvicted of raping his ex-partner in
OL,19,Fan attack which saw him murder her and
OL,20,Fher sister with a crossbow and their
OL,21,Fmother with a butcher's knife.
