OL,7,FThe 26-year-old was found guilty by a
OL,8,Fjury at Cambridge Crown Court after
OL,9,Faround 45 minutes ` accepting the
OL,10,Fprosecution's case that the rape on
OL,11,FLouise Hunt was a "violent, sexual act
OL,12,Fof spite".
OL,14,FClifford was tried in his absence
OL,15,Fafter refusing to leave his cell at
OL,16,FHMP Belmarsh, the court was told.
