OL,7,FThe defendant became "enraged" when
OL,8,Fhis 25-year-old ex-girlfriend Louise
OL,9,Fended their 18-month relationship, and
OL,10,Fconsequently "carefully" planned the
OL,11,Fmurders that happened on July 9.
OL,13,FClifford gained access to the family
OL,14,Fhome by deceiving 61-year-old Carol
OL,15,FHunt, the wife of BBC racing
OL,16,Fcommentator John Hunt, before stabbing
OL,17,Fher to death in a "brutal knife
OL,18,Fattack".
