OL,7,FAfter killing Carol, the defendant
OL,8,Fthen "lay in wait" for an hour for
OL,9,FLouise to enter the house, before
OL,10,Frestraining, raping and ultimately
OL,11,Fmurdering her with a crossbow.
OL,13,FHe then fatally shot 28-year-old
OL,14,FHannah Hunt when she returned to the
OL,15,Fproperty in the quiet cul-de-sac of
OL,16,FAshlyn Close in Bushey, Hertfordshire,
OL,17,Fafter work.
