OL,7,FClifford previously admitted three
OL,8,Fcounts of murder, one of false
OL,9,Fimprisonment against Louise, and two
OL,10,Fcounts of possession of offensive
OL,11,Fweapons ` the crossbow and the knife.
OL,13,FProsecutors said the "violent misogyny
OL,14,Fpromoted" by controversial social
OL,15,Fmedia influencer Andrew Tate "fuelled"
OL,16,FClifford's attacks.
