OL,7,FA solicitor representing four British
OL,8,Fwomen taking action against Tate in
OL,9,Fthe UK has said this information
OL,10,Fshould serve as a "wake up call" for
OL,11,Fsocial media companies who still give
OL,12,Fthe influencer a platform.
OL,14,F"Hearing that Kyle Clifford watched
OL,15,Fvideos of Andrew Tate in the lead up
OL,16,Fto his murders of his ex-girlfriend,
OL,17,Fher mother and sister, is deeply
OL,18,Fupsetting to us, but sadly not
OL,19,Fsurprising," she said.
